                    <div class="col-md-10">
                        <h2>Set up targeted notifications</h2>
                        <p>Azure Service Health integrates into Azure Monitor to notify you and your teams via email or webhook when your business-critical resources are affected.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cognitive-figure">
                    <div class="col-md-2 ash-pad-img">
